{"tid":795307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港眾志成員廣州遭國安帶走扣查 下午記招交代","createTime":"2018-08-27T02:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T14:44:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ea833d216a20b099d0abdd8a250169b87cd6a680","tid":795307,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"香港眾志表示，該黨兩名成員在廣州曾被國安強行帶走及扣留。該黨今天下午將開記招交代。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，上述成員已安全返港，以往亦未曾被捕。基於個人及安全考慮，眾志暫不會安排他們在今天的記招露面。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志今早以「譴責國安兩度扣留眾志成員」為題發採訪通知，指兩名成員分別於今年三月和八月，在內地返港期間，「在廣州被國安強行帶走及扣留盤問」。眾志斥有關國安濫權禁錮並侵犯人身自由，該黨徵詢法律意見後決定今天召開記招公佈詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180827/58611718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180827%2F58611718&d=eDY9MeOsLDH5TAEBpwGg10zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=d485e8b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180827%2F58611718&h=9f4e394d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180827/58611718</a>"},{"pid":"dceb55e2cbae0a2196ccf9fbb296046845ad1055","tid":795307,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:14:10.000Z","msg":"香港中箭去廣州仲乜？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3729954dd8d49c3d3158e75ba9bc9868200f0255","tid":795307,"uid":14103,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:17:04.000Z","msg":"番大陸做乜"},{"pid":"158f8b64ea35120db1e3a4514043dd2f7077a826","tid":795307,"uid":13663,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"是咪上去飲喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffa5b34695b9d26170d61fcc8f188ecbabafd99","tid":795307,"uid":37733,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3729954dd8d49c3d3158e75ba9bc9868200f0255","tid":795307,"uid":14103,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:17:04.000Z","msg":"番大陸做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:20:31.000Z","msg":"述職？"},{"pid":"7aedea8b5986411ee4c35b9a9480be4460d31297","tid":795307,"uid":55488,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:21:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6726f717d21ca39930dbc6a7340085afd0068b59","tid":795307,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"158f8b64ea35120db1e3a4514043dd2f7077a826","tid":795307,"uid":13663,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"是咪上去飲喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"我做係大中華膠上腦, 派人去聲援個「乜乜廣州工人示威」<br />\n<br />\n之前話全支那國好多大學都派人去嘛"},{"pid":"80bb9d5e35aa55110112a2366693f3a4ce1cf781","tid":795307,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:24:11.000Z","msg":"係咪呢單野呀？<br />\n<br />\n香港中箭就係個「境外勢力」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">內地大學生赴深圳聲援工運被捕 官媒批境外勢力操控</span></strong><br />\n2018-08-26 15:03<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5b8250dde603832411e8966f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5b8250dde603832411e8966f&d=eDY9MeOsLDH5TAEBpwGg10zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=3aa3fac0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5b8250dde603832411e8966f</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.tvb.com/ti_img/inews/20180826/entries_5b8250dde603832411e8966f_3533817679_big_1535267886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.tvb.com%2Fti_img%2Finews%2F20180826%2Fentries_5b8250dde603832411e8966f_3533817679_big_1535267886.jpg&h=a49086fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地多間大學的學生到深圳，聲援一間科技公司工運，警方日前採取行動把數十名學生拘捕。官方媒體把矛頭指向境外勢力，學生否認受境外勢力操控。<br />\n<br />\n一批防暴警察星期五清晨持盾闖入廣東惠陽附近一間住宅，拘捕數十名工人和聲援工運的學生。<br />\n<br />\n事緣多名佳士科技公司工人不滿待遇，試圖組建工會，七月中遭公安以尋釁滋事罪刑事拘留。消息傳出後，十六間各地大學數千名學生在網上聯署，要求釋放工人。<br />\n<br />\n一批學生赴深圳聲援，並上街示威。他們有來自中國人民大學、北京外國語大學、北京科技大學和湖南大學等，帶頭的是北大畢業生岳昕。<br />\n<br />\n北大畢業生岳昕表示：「工人們出了這些事情，和我們學生、和我們畢業生有甚麼關係？我跟他們講一句話，今天的學生就是明天的工人，工人們的孩子們又成為明日的學生。」<br />\n<br />\n他們自稱是左翼青年，八月以來在深圳、惠州一帶，舉起毛澤東像遊行，並在街頭演講。<br />\n<br />\n有聲援學生稱：「深圳、廣州這些城市是我們勞動者辛辛苦苦建立起來的，可是我們的工人兄弟在這裡到底遭到了甚麼待遇？」<br />\n<br />\n另一名聲援學生指：「還給我們扣到很多帽子，說甚麼境外勢力，我們都不知道甚麼叫境外勢力。」<br />\n<br />\n亦有聲援學生稱：「我們相信這是中國的工人階級反抗壓迫鬥爭的新篇章，我們相信這是進步的青年學生和工人階級結合的偉大嘗試。」<br />\n<br />\n報道指，他們的行動得到左派網站「烏有之鄉」的中共黨員和退休幹部到場參加。<br />\n<br />\n學生被捕後，官方媒體相繼發表文章，其中新華社指，事件背後有人推波助瀾，包括受境外組織「勞動力」資助的「打工者中心」，而「勞動力」背後有西方非政府組織支持。聲援團體在社交網站指與境外勢力無關，批評說法是抹黑。"},{"pid":"31fa374986d0b692d71cc8294ffc411b635931e0","tid":795307,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158f8b64ea35120db1e3a4514043dd2f7077a826","tid":795307,"uid":13663,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"是咪上去飲喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:28:34.000Z","msg":"屌, 可能真係只係去飲喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">眾志兩成員廣州被國安扣查　事發3月及8月</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180827/s00001/1535331847700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180827%2Fs00001%2F1535331847700&d=eDY9MeOsLDH5TAEBpwGg10zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=048d80bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180827%2Fs00001%2F1535331847700&h=73835b47\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180827/s00001/1535331847700</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180827/s00001/b967c898ced14acb4a01efbc92ee6879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180827%2Fs00001%2Fb967c898ced14acb4a01efbc92ee6879.jpg&h=080d211e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港眾志表示，兩名成員分別在今年3月和8月由大陸返港期間，在廣州被國安強行帶走及扣留盤問。據了解，兩人並非知名眾志成員，現況安全。眾志斥國安濫權禁錮侵犯人身自由，將於下午召開記者會交代詳情。"},{"pid":"83c7e1cfb072be0a140d0146ed183984536d6c86","tid":795307,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6726f717d21ca39930dbc6a7340085afd0068b59","tid":795307,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"158f8b64ea35120db1e3a4514043dd2f7077a826","tid":795307,"uid":13663,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"是咪上去飲喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"我做係大中華膠上腦, 派人去聲援個「乜乜廣州工人示威」<br />\n<br />\n之前話全支那國好多大學都派人去嘛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:29:26.000Z","msg":"指兩名成員分別於今年三月和八月，在內地返港期間，「在廣州被國安強行帶走及扣留盤問」。<br />\n<br />\n八月可能係<br />\n三月應該其他原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2775c11765f2302c9ca7aa09332a7902da02a68b","tid":795307,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"鄰國既事又關你事"},{"pid":"d9117586ae607cd8a25ed5c446780428f9a69f65","tid":795307,"uid":202698,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"返得大陸，預左啦呀哇？怪邊個？"},{"pid":"137a216acb5cb5edbcf5031ef6e23aab3323bf6b","tid":795307,"uid":78222,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9117586ae607cd8a25ed5c446780428f9a69f65","tid":795307,"uid":202698,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"返得大陸，預左啦呀哇？怪邊個？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"咁你姐係認同支那亂鳩拉人係合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n你咁諗都啱嘅  解決提出問題個條友就解決到問題架啦嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hk